    1. 安装apr-util：

  • tar zxvf apr-util-1.5.4.tar.gz

  • cd apr-util-1.5.4

  • ./configure –prefix=/usr/local/apr-util –with-apr=/usr/local/apr

  • make

  • make install

  • ![计算机生成了可选文字: root坦centos6pcre一8.381#mokeInstall.

    1. 安装httpd：

  • tar zxvf httpd-2.4.26.tar.gz

  • cd httpd-2.4.26/

  • ./configure –with-apr=/usr/local/apr –with-apr-util=/usr/local/apr-util –with-pcre=/usr/local/pcre –prefix=/usr/local/httpd –enable-so –enable-rewrite

  • make

    1. 安装PHP：

  • tar zxvf php-7.1.10.tar.gz

  • cd php-7.1.10

  • ./configure –prefix=/usr/local/php –with-apxs2=/usr/local/httpd/bin/apxs –with-curl=/usr/lib –with-freetype-dir=/usr/include/freetype2/freetype/ –with-gd –with-gettext –with-iconv-dir –with-kerberos –with-libdir=lib64 –with-libxml-dir=/usr/local/lib –with-mysqli –with-openssl –with-pcre-regex –with-pdo-mysql –with-pdo-sqlite –with-pear –with-png-dir –with-jpeg-dir –with-xmlrpc –with-xsl –with-zlib –enable-fpm –enable-bcmath –enable-libxml –enable-inline-optimization –enable-gd-native-ttf –enable-mbregex –enable-mbstring –enable-opcache –enable-pcntl –enable-shmop –enable-soap –enable-sockets –enable-sysvsem –enable-xml –enable-zip –enable-calendar –enable-maintainer-zts

  • make

  • make install

    1. 修改配置文件：

  • cp php.ini-development /usr/local/php/lib/php.ini

  • cp /usr/local/php/etc/php-fpm.conf.default /usr/local/php/etc/php-fpm.conf

  • cp /usr/local/php/etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf.default /usr/local/php/etc/php-fpm.d/www.conf

  • cp -R /home/lampz/php-7.1.10/sapi/fpm/php-fpm /etc/init.d/php-fpm

  • vim /usr/local/httpd/conf/httpd.conf

    1. 安装MySQL

  • tar zxvf mysql-5.7.23-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64.tar.gz

  • mv mysql-5.7.23-linux-glibc2.12-x86_64 /home/lampz/mysql 改名字（把mysql-5.7.23……改成mysql）

  • mv mysql /usr/local/ 移动到指定目录

    1. 创建用户及用户组并修改权限

  • cd /usr/local/mysql/

  • groupadd mysql

  • useradd -r -g mysql -s /bin/false mysql

  • chown -R mysql .

  • chgrp -R mysql .

  • mkdir -p /home/mysqldata

  • chown mysql:mysql /home/mysqldata

    1. 编辑环境变量

  • vim /etc/profile

  • 增加

  • PATH=$PATH:/usr/local/mysql/bin

  • 执行source /etc/profile命令

  • 增加：

  • 执行：

    1. 编辑配置文件

  • vim /etc/my.cnf

  • 全删除更换为：

  • # MySQL 5.7

  • [client]

  • port = 3306

  • socket = /home/mysqldata/mysql.sock

  • default-character-set = utf8

  • [mysql]

  • no-auto-rehash

  • default-character-set = utf8

  • [mysqld]

  • # *** base parameters

  • user = mysql

  • port = 3306

  • basedir = /usr/local/mysql

  • datadir = /home/mysqldata

  • socket = /home/mysqldata/mysql.sock

  • pid-file = /home/mysqldata/mysql.pid

  • character-set-server = utf8

  • collation_server = utf8_general_ci

  • default_password_lifetime = 0

  • sql_mode = ‘’

  • # *** log settings

  • log-error = /home/mysqldata/error.log

  • log_timestamps = SYSTEM

  • log_error_verbosity = 3

  • [mysqldump]

  • quick

  • max_allowed_packet = 32M

  • [myisamchk]

  • read_buffer = 8M

  • write_buffer = 8M

  • [mysqld_safe]

  • open-files-limit = 8192

  • log-error = /home/mysqldata/error.log

  • pid-file = /home/mysqldata/mysql.pid

    1. 创建启动程序软链接

  • ln -s /usr/local/mysql/support-files/mysql.server /etc/init.d/mysql

    1. 初始化数据库

  • cd /user/local/mysql/bin

  • ./mysqld –initialize

    1. 使用默认密码，登录数据库

  • mysql -uroot -p -hlocalhost

    1. 如果service mysqld start无法启动，可能是默认启动的是系统自带的5.1版本mysql。

  • 要KILL掉所有mysql进程 再用5.7的绝对路径启动。5.7的绝对路径启动是：/usr/local/mysql/bin/mysql -uroot

    1. 设置mysql用户名密码

  • set password for ‘root’@’localhost’=password(‘root’);

    1. 安装ZABBIX

  • tar zxvf zabbix-4.0.5.tar.gz

  • cd zabbix-4.0.5

  • ./configure –prefix=/usr/local/zabbix –enable-server –enable-agent –with-mysql –enable-ipv6 –with-net-snmp –with-libcurl –with-libxml2 –with-ssh2 –with-openssl

  • 安装缺失的包：

  • yum install libss2-devel libevent-devel

  • 之后再编译，这里可能需要手敲进去，避免有多余字符。

  • make install

  • ![计算机生成了可选文字: NOrun•makeinstall ThankyouforusingZabbix! ．：http：／／“abbx还om> rootgentos6zabbix-4.€.51#makestau•

    1. 创建用户及用户组

  • groupadd zabbix

  • useradd -g zabbix zabbix

    1. 编译配置文件

  • vim /usr/local/zabbix/etc/zabbix_server.conf

  • DBName=zabbix

  • DBUser=zabbix

  • DBPassword=zabbix

  • DBSocket=/usr/local/mysql/data/mysql.sock

  • DBPort=3306

    1. 创建zabbxi数据库

  • CREATE DATABASE zabbix;
